<plot>Lalo tells the hilarious story of a NYC Mexican delivery worker, who upon discovering he's jeopardized his employment, learns that he's been given one last delivery to salvage his job. Faced with a suddenly destroyed bicycle, Lalo is forced to make the desperate decision to steal the "little pink bike" from a nearby 10 yr old Caucasian girl, furious with her hysterical Haitian nanny. With them in hot pursuit, Lalo encounters a Chinese delivery guy and a hip pimped out Punk Rock Messenger. What ensues is a "race to the death" complete with stop motion animated soldiers, fortune cookie road spikes, border patrolled finish lines and a mission to save his job with one last delivery</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?318501</url></doc>
